      "full_name": "Bregan Yauheni Anatolevich",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Yauheni Bregan is a Belarusian judge of the Brest Regional Court. He was appointed by Aliaksandr Lukashenka. He was formerly a judge of the Moskovsky District Court of Brest and judge of the city of Baranovichi in the Brest region. He issued sentences against a large number of citizens of Belarus accused, amongst other things, of having taken part in the protests against the Belarusian regime in August 2020.",
